Classification: Documentary
Genre: Celebrities | Comedy
Status: New Series
Network: BBC TWO ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Wednesdays at 09:00 pm
Runtime: 60 Minutes
Premiere: January 16, 2013

Funny Business takes a look at how some of the country's best comedians can make a fortune from performing at corporate gigs, making dinner speeches and taking part in television commercials.
